    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof, and minor dings on the passenger doors. The interior shows visible wear on the upholstery and some staining on the carpets. All major mechanical systems are functional, though the engine shows signs of age and may require maintenance soon.",
