    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine has significant leaks and struggles to maintain a consistent idle, while the transmission slips frequently when shifting into higher gears. Externally, the body shows heavy wear with several noticeable dents and areas of rust, and the interior upholstery is heavily stained and torn. It is recommended that the buyer brings a trailer, as the car is not currently reliable for long-distance driving.",
